summary: Loneliness stretched out in front of him, endless and continuous as nature’s cycles. In the beauty of this place, there was a...
caption:
Loneliness stretched out in front of him, endless and continuous as nature’s cycles. In the beauty of this place, there was a darkness, crawling and scraping into the little haven of the temple. 

It twisted and turned into his mind, burrowing into his dreams. This place was not safe, the thorns tore into the peace of the forest decimating everything in it’s path. He would be next. 

 The fear of staying wormed into his gut but he was terrified of leaving. His dreams offered no solace. So he waited - bags packed and ready - for a sign.

summary: Don’t think about how Molly used to wake Fjord up from his nightmares!! Especially don’t think about the first time he has a...
body: Don’t think about how Molly used to wake Fjord up from his nightmares!! Especially don’t think about the first time he has a nightmare when rooming with Caduceus!! And Caduceus shakes him awake when he hears Fjord groaning and thrashing around, and it’s dark and Fjord is confused as he comes out of the nightmare and for just a second he thinks it’s Molly there with him again. And then he blinks, and Molly is gone, it’s only Caduceus’ scruffy face frowning down at him in concern. Because Molly is gone, and Fjord can never get him back. Definitely don’t think about that!!!!
